net.bramp.unsafe.bytebuddy

Enum MethodVariableStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<MethodVariableStore>
      • net.bramp.unsafe.bytebuddy.MethodVariableStore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<MethodVariableStore>

    public enum MethodVariableStore
extends Enum<MethodVariableStore>
    A stack assignment that stores a method variable from a given index of the local variable array.

    This class is a copy of MethodVariableLoader with a few things changed to make it suitable for storing.
